<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-light">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <p class="text-highlight font-medium text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-3">About</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">
      The short version
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
      <p>
        I'm a consultant based in Dubai with 12+ years in enterprise systems. I started
        my career in Oracle HCM consulting, spent three years at Oracle itself, and
        eventually moved into senior roles leading large-scale digital transformations
        for government authorities, banks, and multinationals across the MENA region.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over the years I've worked with 20+ organizations across 8 countries &mdash;
        from the Digital Dubai Authority and the National Bank of Egypt to petroleum
        companies in Kuwait and healthcare institutions in Qatar. That range taught me
        that technology only works when it fits the people and processes it serves.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today, I'm focused on bringing AI and intelligent automation into enterprise
        operations. Not as a buzzword, but as a practical tool &mdash; automating the
        repetitive, surfacing what matters, and giving teams back the time to do
        meaningful work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      {[
        "Oracle Fusion Cloud",
        "Oracle EBS",
        "AI & Automation",
        "Digital Transformation",
        "HCM & Payroll",
        "Systems Integration",
        "SQL & PL/SQL",
        "MENA Region",
      ].map((tag) => (
        <span class="text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-full text-muted">
          {tag}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
